# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SELAH — what does NOT go in the repository
#
# Two principles, and the second one matters more than it looks:
#
#   1. NEVER COMMIT A SECRET. Obvious, and still the most common way a company
#      like this one destroys itself. We will hold Ugandan taxpayers' financial
#      data. A leaked key is not an incident; it is the end.
#
#   2. 🔴 COMMIT EVERYTHING NEEDED TO REPRODUCE THE TESTS.
#      package.json and package-lock.json are NOT noise — they are how a stranger
#      (or you, in six months, on a new laptop) runs `npm test` and gets the same
#      408 assertions. An earlier .gitignore excluded them. Anyone cloning this
#      repo could not have run a single test.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── secrets. Never. ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
credentials*
secrets*
*_rsa
*_ed25519

# 🔴 And never a real taxpayer's data. Not one file, not "just for testing".
# Uganda's DPPA s.9(1) makes financial data SPECIAL PERSONAL DATA — processing is
# PROHIBITED BY DEFAULT, and a digital lender's DIRECTOR was personally convicted
# on 10 July 2025 for failing to register with the PDPO.
#
# There is no such thing as a test file with a real TIN in it.
client-data/
*-CLIENT-*.xlsx
*-CLIENT-*.csv
health-check/completed/

# ── dependencies and build artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.cache/
dist/

# Playwright
test-results/
playwright-report/
blob-report/
.playwright/
ms-playwright/

# ── OS and editor noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json

# ── the raw image drop ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 44 MB of unprocessed source photography. The PROCESSED, compressed images that
# the site actually serves live in platform/web/assets/images/ and ARE committed.
#
# 🔴 AND BEFORE ANY OF THESE GO LIVE: we do not know that we have the rights to
# them. See platform/web/assets/images/README.md. We are building a compliance
# company; being sued over an unlicensed photograph would be a spectacularly
# stupid way to prove we do not practise what we sell.
images/

# ── scratch ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.tmp.js
*.bak
.e.tmp
.t.tmp
